Try adding a trailing `/` to the end of your proxy pass:

    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:4000/;

**Without** the trailing `/`, the full path will be passed:&lt;br/&gt;
`http://127.0.0.1:4000/app/something`


**With** the trailing `/`, the location pattern, `/app`, will be replaced with the `/`:&lt;br/&gt;
`http://127.0.0.1:4000/something`

