First, you need to remove the `$`. `$currencyCode` gives you a `Binding&lt;String&gt;`, but you want the value, not the binding to the value. (See [this answer][1] where I explain Binding.)

Second, you want to use a computed property, because your number formatter needs to change based on your selected `currencyCode`. Put this inside your view struct:

    private var currencyFormatter: NumberFormatter {
        let formatter = NumberFormatter()
        formatter.numberStyle = .currency
        formatter.currencyCode = currencyCode
        return formatter
    }

