In absence of other answers, I&#39;ll proceed with a [SFX module for installers][3], by packaging all the three `.exe` at points 1-3 (plus an `install_all.bat` running them in sequence) into a self extracting installer, that will automatically extract all the needed files (certificate included) and finally run the `install_all.bat`


